name: Hantu Jerangkong (Jerangkong)
shortLoreBlurb: Hantu Jerangkong (Jerangkong) is a monster from Java/Indonesia linked to skeleton ghost, night. Mediates with the dead and fate.
overlapsLinks: Anubis (Egyptian), Chandra (Hindu), Chang'e (China), Hel (Norse), Tsukuyomi (Japan), Yama (Buddhist)
